Just some rough order of magnitude numbers for context switch!

Intel 5150: 105ns/syscall
Intel E5440: 87ns/syscall
Intel E5520: 58ns/syscall
Intel X5550: 52ns/syscall
Intel L5630: 58ns/syscall
Intel E5-2620: 67ns/syscall

(http://blog.tsunanet.net/2010/11/how-long-does-it-take-to-make-context.html)

Proof earliest-deadline-first is optimal:
http://www.cs.fsu.edu/~baker/realtime/restricted/notes/edfscheduling.html
